00:39:49,516 --> 00:39:51,193
It's meant for people
to wear to food stalls.

836
00:39:51,276 --> 00:39:52,433
It costs 55 yuan

837
00:39:52,516 --> 00:39:54,355
from top to bottom.
And, it's disposable.

838
00:39:54,476 --> 00:39:55,313
By the way,

839
00:39:55,396 --> 00:39:56,875
it's 80 yuan if you include

840
00:39:57,115 --> 00:39:58,312
this disposable bottle as well.

841
00:39:58,395 --> 00:39:59,916
What? You use Taobao too?

842
00:40:00,276 --> 00:40:02,016
I had no choice. You forced me to do it.

843
00:40:02,395 --> 00:40:03,436
That's pretty good.

844
00:40:03,555 --> 00:40:05,355
Share the link with me later.

845
00:40:08,436 --> 00:40:09,593
By the way, I have something to tell you.

846
00:40:09,676 --> 00:40:11,590
The Dragon Boat Festival
is a public holiday.

847
00:40:11,875 --> 00:40:13,552
Our tuition class

848
00:40:13,635 --> 00:40:14,673
will be suspended for the time being.

849
00:40:14,756 --> 00:40:15,756
But why?

850
00:40:16,075 --> 00:40:17,155
Are you going on a trip?

851
00:40:17,875 --> 00:40:19,916
I'm going to join the TCM forum.

852
00:40:20,276 --> 00:40:21,633
But your name wasn't included

853
00:40:21,716 --> 00:40:22,633
in the name list.

854
00:40:22,716 --> 00:40:24,232
Besides, people won't invite

855
00:40:24,315 --> 00:40:25,953
half-baked physicians like us.

856
00:40:26,036 --> 00:40:27,036
This time,

857
00:40:27,555 --> 00:40:30,196
I'm going there because
the organiser invited me.

858
00:40:30,716 --> 00:40:32,555
What gives?
Why didn't he invite me then?

859
00:40:32,916 --> 00:40:35,113
The organiser is an

860
00:40:35,196 --> 00:40:36,073
old client of mine.

861
00:40:36,156 --> 00:40:38,272
I'm going there to visit him mainly.

862
00:40:38,355 --> 00:40:40,660
I'm just joining the forum
since I'll be there anyway.

863
00:40:41,795 --> 00:40:44,196
I think you're just going there
to join the forum.

864
00:40:45,196 --> 00:40:46,196
Take me with you.

865
00:40:47,036 --> 00:40:48,312
A spy like me

866
00:40:48,395 --> 00:40:51,352
needs to head to the enemy's nest
to eradicate them once and for all.

867
00:40:52,196 --> 00:40:53,153
Take me with you.

868
00:40:53,236 --> 00:40:54,033
You're a renowned figure.

869
00:40:54,116 --> 00:40:55,769
You need to have a servant beside you.

870
00:40:56,395 --> 00:40:57,476
Besides,

871
00:40:57,956 --> 00:40:59,652
the mountain path is rugged and uneven.

872
00:41:00,196 --> 00:41:01,153
I checked the schedule too.

873
00:41:01,236 --> 00:41:01,953
We have to gather mugwort

874
00:41:02,036 --> 00:41:02,874
in the mountains before dawn
on the second day.

875
00:41:02,957 --> 00:41:04,312
I'm sure you'll depart at night.

876
00:41:04,395 --> 00:41:05,673
What if you encounter a bear

877
00:41:05,756 --> 00:41:07,795
or a robber? It'll be dangerous.

878
00:41:08,516 --> 00:41:09,716
Most importantly,

879
00:41:11,236 --> 00:41:12,153
it's a long journey.

880
00:41:12,236 --> 00:41:14,635
You need a second driver somehow.

881
00:41:21,882 --> 00:41:23,197
(The prescriptions and remedies
used in this drama)

882
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:25,157
(are referenced from relevant
traditional Chinese medicine books)

883
00:41:25,240 --> 00:41:27,545
(Do not use without medical advice)
(End of Episode 9)

